{"id": 1217, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于信用卡，你有什么不满的吗？", "description": "最让我不爽的就是，花钱比原来更大手大脚。（题图来自：Polly Fern）", "record_count": 2628, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160912233158boWPY5sUdQKmwNeI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-21T03:00:55Z", "options": [{"id": 118034, "content": "谁能告诉我怎么拥有一张信用卡？", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766614}, {"id": 120321, "content": "怎么刷都没有积分", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776724}, {"id": 121617, "content": "办卡要钱吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773447}, {"id": 118036, "content": "一张卡有十几种特权，但其实只有一两种有用．．．", "image": null, "praise_count": 214, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 486682}, {"id": 118037, "content": "最不爽的是，刷了还要还", "image": null, "praise_count": 345, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766620}, {"id": 118038, "content": "老子有钱！还得起！老子不要分期！别烦我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 333, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590050}, {"id": 118039, "content": "业务什么的太复杂，用得不踏实", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766624}, {"id": 118040, "content": "最让人不爽的是会推销保险", "image": null, "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 750435}, {"id": 118041, "content": "招行20块钱积一分！", "image": null, "praise_count": 134, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 509270}, {"id": 118042, "content": "招行20块钱积一分！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 509270}, {"id": 118043, "content": "助长铺张浪费。", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765611}, {"id": 118044, "content": "各种推销，出了问题各种推托", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766636}, {"id": 118045, "content": "妈的查不了利息多少", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761062}, {"id": 118046, "content": "好像没什么很有用的特权，最实用的购物返现打折什么的很少很少", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419840}, {"id": 118047, "content": "又多了一堆需要防范的诈骗- -而就算是官方打来的推销电话，听着也挺烦的", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167600}, {"id": 118048, "content": "为薅二十块钱一杯的星巴克，然后多刷几千块钱。捡芝麻丢西瓜的事儿时有发生~", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333763}, {"id": 118049, "content": "每月战战兢兢生怕错过还款时间", "image": "img/option/option/20160921114124BwZVkrb4ajvqfGJi", "praise_count": 148, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118590}, {"id": 118051, "content": "感觉信用卡和支付宝的蚂蚁花呗差不多，只是两者额度会有所不同，两者使用都有一定限制。但是蚂蚁花呗的账单更佳清晰，而信用卡会麻烦一些。对很多人而言，钱对外流出的速度更快一些，毕竟数字的流出比现金流出给人的感觉不同。", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766651}, {"id": 118052, "content": "短信和电话推销特！别！多！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765001}, {"id": 118053, "content": "最大的不满是竟然要还钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667615}, {"id": 118054, "content": "建行汽车卡原始卖点是可以定点免费洗车，可是洗车点越来越少，越来越找不到……而且建行自己可能都不清楚在一个城市还有哪些洗车点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763789}, {"id": 118055, "content": "大多数卡网购不算积分，这不科学啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241724}, {"id": 118056, "content": "真不用提额了！别月月提醒我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760849}, {"id": 118058, "content": "whatever", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736242}, {"id": 118059, "content": "卡越多刷的越多", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766660}, {"id": 118060, "content": "绝大多数优惠活动都用不上，动不动出国满减，动不动高端酒店", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123624}, {"id": 118063, "content": "用完之后，发现根本还不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687299}, {"id": 118064, "content": "卡种太多，权限不一，往往一家银行就好几张卡。能不能只有一张卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739672}, {"id": 118066, "content": "万年额度，永远不升，不过目前来说，够用了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702171}, {"id": 119602, "content": "我很满意。毕竟每个月工资都给它了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773031}, {"id": 118067, "content": "广发银行信用卡设置了小额免支付密码之后刷卡还是要输密码", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711434}, {"id": 118069, "content": "钱花的更多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649788}, {"id": 118070, "content": "为什么很多银行的信用卡积分不能折换成刷卡机金来还帐单，一定要去积分商城换实物（大部分都没用还占地方）", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341204}, {"id": 118071, "content": "用钱感觉不心痛了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 553920}, {"id": 118072, "content": "直接送我进了班房", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 731106}, {"id": 118073, "content": "最不爽的是，出了账单后，想不起自己买了啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 144, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766724}, {"id": 118075, "content": "一看账单就很郁闷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 731676}, {"id": 118076, "content": "我凭自己本事借的钱，为什么要还！", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766273}, {"id": 118077, "content": "看着密密麻麻的账单，完全想不起自己买了啥。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766731}, {"id": 118078, "content": "不刷吧，要收年费，刷吧，要定期还，总吧，说你恶意透支，不用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669607}, {"id": 118079, "content": "感觉要砍手的节奏，等我还完！老子要销卡！销卡！销卡！???", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 398234}, {"id": 118080, "content": "每次都信誓旦旦我要把卡掰了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766741}, {"id": 118081, "content": "每个月都有那么几天不舒服", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 764171}, {"id": 118082, "content": "我婆婆一想破坏我婆婆婆媳儿子儿媳色一二一二 wei andwei 想而已\n我婆婆一想破坏我婆婆婆媳儿子儿媳色一二一二 wei andwei 想而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 619785}, {"id": 118083, "content": "忘记了没卡的日子。已经不能想象没信用卡怎么生活的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 762397}, {"id": 118084, "content": "无法充分体验不同卡带来的实惠 变成网银工具了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752705}, {"id": 119620, "content": "还的还", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773125}, {"id": 118085, "content": "卡不少，常用的就一张，其余的忘了刷5次就几百块年费。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 376515}, {"id": 118086, "content": "自从办了信用卡，我就成了月光族", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169452}, {"id": 118087, "content": "权益自选模式，不希望为了权益永远在开新卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741711}]}